==== Timeline

    - *Year 1*: Institutional setup, IRB approval, equipment procurement, pilot phase (n=10)
    - *Year 2*: Main enrollment (target n=36 additional ME/CFS patients and 36 controls)
    - *Year 3*: Final data collection, analysis, manuscript preparation
    - *Publication plan*: 4–5 papers targeting *Nature Medicine*, *Lancet Neurology*, *Brain*, *Journal of Applied Physiology*

